Substitution rules:

The suffixes must be included in the .SUFFIXES list.

General format:

.src.dst:
	suffix rule


$< refers to the source
$@ refers to the destination

$(var:op%os=np%ns)
  replace the content of var by replacing op with np and os with ns.

--------------

makeimages: main makefile, how to do image packaging
makerules: generic make rules, say to generate .o from .c
makevar: to put additional defines there

src.mk: Use ifeq($(OS), qnx) to define additional defines

